description: The elimination rounds of our Summer Smackdown Tournament are coming to an end, thus far, Jessie "Cut-Throat" Colter, Eli "The Hammer" Hunter & Mitch "The Machine" Vaughn have all secured their positions in the quarter final rounds, but only one space remains. Enter muscled gods, Marcus "Titan" Ruhl & Billy "The BodySlam" Santoro going toe to toe for sexual dominancy. With overall muscle on their side, these two hunks think they each have what it takes to steal the gold belt this year. Titan may have the weight advantage on his opponent but BodySlam is more than confident his vicious leg locks will win him the victory this match. Which of these hunks will prove to be the victor and move one step closer to earning the title of champion? While the other has his ass kicked out of the tournament with a face full of cum.
title: Naked Kombat's Summer Smackdown Tournament - Elimination Round 4
